#: app/data/card_manifest.py:25
msgid ""
"Unlimited attack technology on Destroyers. Existing DDs instantly get the"
" ability to have Attack technology greater than their Hull Size because "
"of this card, but they still must be retrofitted with that technology "
"normally (Attack 2 or Attack 3)."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:32
msgid "Polytitanium Alloy"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:33
msgid "DDs cost 2 less."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:40
msgid "Long Lance Torpedo"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:41
msgid ""
"All of this player's DDs fire as B-Class instead of D-Class (Alternate "
"Empire DDs fire as B-Class instead of C-Class). This doesn't apply in "
"terrain where they would fire as E-Class (5.8)."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:43
msgid "(Alternate Empire DDs fire as B-Class instead of C-Class)"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:50
