msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:83
msgid ""
"CAs take 1 extra hit to kill. However, their Hull Size does not increase "
"because of this card: it is still considered 2 (barring other card "
"effects). This does not help them against boarding attacks."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:85 app/data/card_manifest.py:93
msgid "When a CA is present in combat."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/card_manifest.py:90
