#: app/data/scenarios.py:1786
msgid ""
"8.1.9 Hidden Galactic Capitol - DM Scenario Variant\n"
"Setup as per 2.9 shuffling the GC counter in with DS counters and placing"
" in the blue dot hexes. Place the WP in any non-blue dot hex adjacent to "
"one of the player home systems. Instead of using the table in 8.3.3 for "
"DM entry, roll 1d10 and place the DM on the hex matching the result. All "
"other setup is per the above scenario."
